itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T05:01:41.000Z","msg":"死左即係留低晒啲問題比人地 自殺係好唔負責既行為 自己既事自己點解唔去解決?<br />\nsorry for 認真左"},{"pid":"4a6af523b329db24a459a125eaa12f8b4da60a99","tid":151004,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T05:03:25.000Z","msg":"其實每一個人都喺度自殺緊，大家都知道人生最好係死亡但冇設法諗辦法去阻止死亡，其實同自殺冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f5e342c6228add4787e7e18d8ad7ade05266ba","tid":151004,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T05:04:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實每一個人都喺度自殺緊，大家都知道人生最<span style=\"color: red;\">後</span>係死亡但冇設法諗辦法去阻止死亡，其實同自殺冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"af75539dceffaa75db6598c27a2e63308f6d9256","tid":151004,"uid":26766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T05:07:26.000Z","msg":"唔開心自殺無乜問題,點解要逼人地生存,你又唔係佢你唔會了解佢有幾痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2569fde0d1df8c466ebfb9aa69d3a41f36adc3d8","tid":151004,"uid":73935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T05:09:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打空針</blockquote><br />\n打完會點</blockquote> <br />\n動身安樂死都好似係打空針"},{"pid":"9393d16414b4c3459c72c5e6571c63a9974c47f6","tid":151004,"uid":3742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T05:11:03.000Z","msg":"吊頸 完全自殺手冊有講"},{"pid":"7d3fd10be23cdc5af96621b63bbf1fc7b213504e","tid":151004,"uid":85619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T05:54:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔開心自殺無乜問題,點解要逼人地生存,你又唔係佢你唔會了解佢有幾痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無人有逼過任何人生存，生存係每個人既選擇，我地而家做嘅，只係勸下有自殺念頭既人，希望佢地諗清楚自殺係咪真係唯一既選擇<br />\n利申 覺得生存有時都幾辛苦，但一諗起自己仲有好多野未試未做，再者如果死左會好對唔住屋企人，會令屋企人好傷心之後，即刻唔會再有尋死既念頭。我相信再有錢、生活再無憂既人都有唔開心既時候，都曾經有過自殺既念頭，但係我更相信總有解決問題既方法"},{"pid":"a3dd263e05270a15eed65ee39bc48a27771139c7","tid":151004,"uid":8705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T09:08:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死左即係留低晒啲問題比人地 自殺係好唔負責既行為 自己既事自己點解唔去解決?<br />\nsorry for 認真左</blockquote><br />\n除左父母要洗多一大筆錢我諗唔到留低左咩問題"},{"pid":"df2fc93b64ea75bcdf8d80ced59e817d9c5da755","tid":151004,"uid":8705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T09:08:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔開心自殺無乜問題,點解要逼人地生存,你又唔係佢你唔會了解佢有幾痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩啊"},{"pid":"19d674e90bf3947502114ca6c65f7308e5028527","tid":151004,"uid":8705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T09:09:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吊頸 完全自殺手冊有講</blockquote><br />\n我諗吊頸同跳樓都一樣"},{"pid":"9b6f035cc199258db07ae3c092e6c45a870ef44f","tid":151004,"uid":53126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T09:24:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>吊頸 完全自殺手冊有講</blockquote><br />\n我諗吊頸同跳樓都一樣</blockquote><br />\n點會一樣？<br />\n跳樓幾秒鐘<br />\n吊頸幾分鐘喎！<br />\n最唔舒服既方法就像吊頸"},{"pid":"22296c60cb08be1195ae566720d4834d2a04914b","tid":151004,"uid":62627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T09:32:44.000Z","msg":"有G6PD嘅人自殺好似會簡單d<br />\n但應該唔會舒服得去邊<br />\n利申：有plan過"},{"pid":"7b3a99c9a147227da8961b13df1b041bd22c4a45","tid":151004,"uid":33040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T15:38:47.000Z","msg":"跳樓 落地果下應該即時冇左知覺應該唔痛"},{"pid":"70a616d4c2586a5634659f0e832331d6bd99d41e","tid":151004,"uid":8705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T20:39:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有G6PD嘅人自殺好似會簡單d<br />\n但應該唔會舒服得去邊<br />\n利申：有plan過</blockquote><br />\n咩黎"},{"pid":"b99d6538a1a0037e6f43be620a11840f1c88323f","tid":151004,"uid":47149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T23:32:49.000Z","msg":"早兩晚先研究完 有興趣可以交流下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/12/073241_55dfe1932d08db79b95af8c56fbeae6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F12%2F073241_55dfe1932d08db79b95af8c56fbeae6e.jpg&h=2b989a08&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N6K43wf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN6K43wf.jpg&h=a0c03120&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/12/073242_73aeae6d2b3a6c4d4701093b5c1ae1cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F12%2F073242_73aeae6d2b3a6c4d4701093b5c1ae1cc.jpg&h=e2509d96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04d5cfa5211bb47f46aa7880d0406abfdbc220d9","tid":151004,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T23:44:02.000Z","msg":"bookmarked"},{"pid":"04497fc7fafc0e80b40518b28fd61154886272ea","tid":151004,"uid":6250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T23:45:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食藥</blockquote><br />\n我話你知，食藥死唔去，我嗰隻藥50粒照計係死到，但已經比人救返。所以DO係死唔去只有辛苦同要醒返就要入精神病院，所以唔好食藥<br />\n利申，過來人"},{"pid":"fc2f27a1a1edb209e22cb76b0769403e126c550e","tid":151004,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T00:14:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食藥</blockquote><br />\n我話你知，食藥死唔去，我嗰隻藥50粒照計係死到，但已經比人救返。所以DO係死唔去只有辛苦同要醒返就要入精神病院，所以唔好食藥<br />\n利申，過來人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宜家d藥設計到大量食唔會死<br />\n真正可以量大致命既藥得毒品 <br />\n<br />\n海洛英高劑量可以直接麻醉中樞神經<br />\n同時麻醉呼吸肌 可以係無意識情況下缺氧死"},{"pid":"d1d06402ee34c12e8a3e4a49d3b3336208ea7000","tid":151004,"uid":6250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T00:21:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食藥</blockquote><br />\n我話你知，食藥死唔去，我嗰隻藥50粒照計係死到，但已經比人救返。所以DO係死唔去只有辛苦同要醒返就要入精神病院，所以唔好食藥<br />\n利申，過來人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宜家d藥設計到大量食唔會死<br />\n真正可以量大致命既藥得毒品 <br />\n<br />\n海洛英高劑量可以直接麻醉中樞神經<br />\n同時麻醉呼吸肌 可以係無意識情況下缺氧死</blockquote><br />\n我之前食嗰隻精神科藥係毒藥都比人救返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f05adc2bac3363d5da28e02b69ac88032d8c8fb6","tid":151004,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T00:28:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食藥</blockquote><br />\n我話你知，食藥死唔去，我嗰隻藥50粒照計係死到，但已經比人救返。所以DO係死唔去只有辛苦同要醒返就要入精神病院，所以唔好食藥<br />\n利申，過來人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宜家d藥設計到大量食唔會死<br />\n真正可以量大致命既藥得毒品 <br />\n<br />\n海洛英高劑量可以直接麻醉中樞神經<br />\n同時麻醉呼吸肌 可以係無意識情況下缺氧死</blockquote><br />\n我之前食嗰隻精神科藥係毒藥都比人救返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係毒藥 現代毒藥都設計到大量使用唔會死<br />\n嚴格黎講得傳統毒品先係真正可以自殺到<br />\n<br />\n例如5克海洛英到達致命劑量  <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6w1h708.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6w1h708.jpg&h=5680dd4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12539f66e55a09f7d7c7af8afb9c15da93fb2469","tid":151004,"uid":36329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T00:48:03.000Z","msg":"如果冇一種方法係會舒服嘅樓主係咪唔會去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我認同有啲問題真係點都解決唔到，我絕對認同死根本就可以解決一切問題<br />\n但係亦有啲問題只係你諗唔到點解決，或者有比死亡更好嘅解決方法<br />\n<br />\n依度咁多人，講出來冇人幫到你先再諗自殺？"},{"pid":"9b35a5931fcfbbcfbd65a601a3c74126421adf86","tid":151004,"uid":45645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T00:53:49.000Z","msg":"安眠藥加煤氣，最舒服"},{"pid":"3b2fd7b776857871ac033632c8ec38d1593925d3","tid":151004,"uid":85619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T05:51:23.000Z","msg":"其實呢個post睇到我都幾寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2134f8b8249b8e4577ebd168a189eed4b9f6bfad","tid":151004,"uid":44725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T06:20:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實呢個post睇到我都幾寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係舒服, 開心同解脫<br />\n對於想自殺既人黎講"},{"pid":"92a8469ce6aa1f88d6f96ec3d19b0411d9d477ef","tid":151004,"uid":85619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T06:55:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實呢個post睇到我都幾寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係舒服, 開心同解脫<br />\n對於想自殺既人黎講</blockquote><br />\n正確啲黎講係百感交集<br />\n一方面好心寒，原來真係有咁多人會諗尋死既方法，上面有人直頭講話試過<br />\n另一方面又覺得好惋惜，點解大家真係要去到揀死呢一步黎解決問題<br />\n我明白我唔會理解倒大家既壓力/不滿，但我只係想係度長氣少少咁講多句，希望大家決定尋死前真係三思"},{"pid":"e5fa6a9216d00d4e6028aedbe7e61b81469f3af4","tid":151004,"uid":44725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T07:01:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實呢個post睇到我都幾寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係舒服, 開心同解脫<br />\n對於想自殺既人黎講</blockquote><br />\n正確啲黎講係百感交集<br />\n一方面好心寒，原來真係有咁多人會諗尋死既方法，上面有人直頭講話試過<br />\n另一方面又覺得好惋惜，點解大家真係要去到揀死呢一步黎解決問題<br />\n我明白我唔會理解倒大家既壓力/不滿，但我只係想係度長氣少少咁講多句，希望大家決定尋死前真係三思</blockquote><br />\n我十年前已經想死, 一開始係不斷搵目標鼓勵自己唔好死<br />\n間中有諗過積極生存落去, 但是好快又不停諗想死<br />\n拖下就咁多年真係好辛苦, 到而家都係想死<br />\n如果尋死前要三思, 我應該十思完都係想死"},{"pid":"d002f44527abde32dd7877b40a240596a66e61ee","tid":151004,"uid":8705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:44:28.000Z","msg":"估唔到搵到咁多同路人"},{"pid":"5914d1a44d9118dc9e7d37b691bc3628341476f4","tid":151004,"uid":8705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:45:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果冇一種方法係會舒服嘅樓主係咪唔會去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我認同有啲問題真係點都解決唔到，我絕對認同死根本就可以解決一切問題<br />\n但係亦有啲問題只係你諗唔到點解決，或者有比死亡更好嘅解決方法<br />\n<br />\n依度咁多人，講出來冇人幫到你先再諗自殺？</blockquote><br />\n幫？點幫"},{"pid":"b9eeb32323eeef0411d18517547b2539a16e82cd","tid":151004,"uid":8705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:47:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早兩晚先研究完 有興趣可以交流下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/12/073241_55dfe1932d08db79b95af8c56fbeae6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F12%2F073241_55dfe1932d08db79b95af8c56fbeae6e.jpg&h=2b989a08&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N6K43wf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN6K43wf.jpg&h=a0c03120&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/12/073242_73aeae6d2b3a6c4d4701093b5c1ae1cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F12%2F073242_73aeae6d2b3a6c4d4701093b5c1ae1cc.jpg&h=e2509d96&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nshotgun to head都要1.7分鐘"},{"pid":"e38634b0f10d19b034c0ae792b080dd743468b65","tid":151004,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:01:47.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"b6015b1ee15e5d1cb80d054141bb8089794d65ac","tid":151004,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:08:10.000Z","msg":"shotgun to head應該唔洗1.7分鐘<br />\n<br />\n1.7分鐘應該係指所有腦部細胞死亡時間<br />\n<br />\n其實一開槍已經失去意識"},{"pid":"7718ea4369e744be94488e0bbc0f5ea412fb3695","tid":151004,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:10:17.000Z","msg":"食安眠藥溝酒加開煤氣?"},{"pid":"ae5d168a2f624d83cff0c5e53ea67b28d13e8cc3","tid":151004,"uid":8705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:25:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食安眠藥溝酒加開煤氣?</blockquote><br />\n無地方"},{"pid":"8c000414ec99ad3537cd3639038ea91ffa72fa7e","tid":151004,"uid":36329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T12:35:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果冇一種方法係會舒服嘅樓主係咪唔會去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我認同有啲問題真係點都解決唔到，我絕對認同死根本就可以解決一切問題<br />\n但係亦有啲問題只係你諗唔到點解決，或者有比死亡更好嘅解決方法<br />\n<br />\n依度咁多人，講出來冇人幫到你先再諗自殺？</blockquote><br />\n幫？點幫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你唔講想我點樣答你 你講咗唔一定幫到 你唔講一定幫唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9328514bcfad2b347ac8d98bb1d9b7e79d4fef9b","tid":151004,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:15:13.000Z","msg":"外國有得安樂死"},{"pid":"bed86bee57fdcbffb1507df6eb9948dd1f3b7b4a","tid":151004,"uid":84021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:41:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>外國有得安樂死</blockquote><br />\n唔係咁用法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算荷蘭提倡過既都係俾啲覺得已經過得好滿足，人生目標已達成既人，唔係覺得人生已玩完既人<br />\n人生唔會玩完架，你未睇清整幅圖既全部姐，環境問題，情緒問題令你將佢focus係黑暗既一邊，你咪忽略左光明個邊，但佢係度架，需要花時間先會睇到，慢慢黎啦"},{"pid":"650c0a241787bc7e6322af4f8574cfb4966daa73","tid":151004,"uid":85619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T00:34:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實呢個post睇到我都幾寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係舒服, 開心同解脫<br />\n對於想自殺既人黎講</blockquote><br />\n正確啲黎講係百感交集<br />\n一方面好心寒，原來真係有咁多人會諗尋死既方法，上面有人直頭講話試過<br />\n另一方面又覺得好惋惜，點解大家真係要去到揀死呢一步黎解決問題<br />\n我明白我唔會理解倒大家既壓力/不滿，但我只係想係度長氣少少咁講多句，希望大家決定尋死前真係三思</blockquote><br />\n我十年前已經想死, 一開始係不斷搵目標鼓勵自己唔好死<br />\n間中有諗過積極生存落去, 但是好快又不停諗想死<br />\n拖下就咁多年真係好辛苦, 到而家都係想死<br />\n如果尋死前要三思, 我應該十思完都係想死</blockquote><br />\n咁你靜係想都好少少，佢地有人真係試過，好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e854b18b933ca2cf382a2b612d802aa588ad9f5","tid":151004,"uid":85619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T00:36:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果冇一種方法係會舒服嘅樓主係咪唔會去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我認同有啲問題真係點都解決唔到，我絕對認同死根本就可以解決一切問題<br />\n但係亦有啲問題只係你諗唔到點解決，或者有比死亡更好嘅解決方法<br />\n<br />\n依度咁多人，講出來冇人幫到你先再諗自殺？</blockquote><br />\n幫？點幫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你唔講想我點樣答你 你講咗唔一定幫到 你唔講一定幫唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係，樓豬講都未講個問題就問人點幫，人地點知你個問題係咩啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b24f391529adea82da02120d4b3dae880bdc54b9","tid":151004,"uid":85619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T00:37:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>外國有得安樂死</blockquote><br />\n唔係咁用法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算荷蘭提倡過既都係俾啲覺得已經過得好滿足，人生目標已達成既人，唔係覺得人生已玩完既人<br />\n人生唔會玩完架，你未睇清整幅圖既全部姐，環境問題，情緒問題令你將佢focus係黑暗既一邊，你咪忽略左光明個邊，但佢係度架，需要花時間先會睇到，慢慢黎啦</blockquote><br />\n岩呀岩呀，呢個post需要多啲正能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4759c648c3c21ba17a2f23bd6cff33541b718b8f","tid":151004,"uid":41138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T02:19:03.000Z","msg":"去成人台體驗下先好死"},{"pid":"dcfe6d778cf8f597700faec819d50ccda44cf442","tid":151004,"uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T02:37:57.000Z","msg":"死都唔想累到人，我真係唔知點先死到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd3e43faab683dcabdb3daa5e8c0c941798dcec","tid":151004,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T05:06:57.000Z","msg":"餓死"},{"pid":"d4ecf406196e146aa105c8a1ffa80624785c28d8","tid":151004,"uid":44725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T14:03:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實呢個post睇到我都幾寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係舒服, 開心同解脫<br />\n對於想自殺既人黎講</blockquote><br />\n正確啲黎講係百感交集<br />\n一方面好心寒，原來真係有咁多人會諗尋死既方法，上面有人直頭講話試過<br />\n另一方面又覺得好惋惜，點解大家真係要去到揀死呢一步黎解決問題<br />\n我明白我唔會理解倒大家既壓力/不滿，但我只係想係度長氣少少咁講多句，希望大家決定尋死前真係三思</blockquote><br />\n我十年前已經想死, 一開始係不斷搵目標鼓勵自己唔好死<br />\n間中有諗過積極生存落去, 但是好快又不停諗想死<br />\n拖下就咁多年真係好辛苦, 到而家都係想死<br />\n如果尋死前要三思, 我應該十思完都係想死</blockquote><br />\n咁你靜係想都好少少，佢地有人真係試過，好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我食過藥丸, 一隻腳企出花槽, 用毛巾打圈綁係浴室近天花支柱上面<br />\n算唔算靜係想?"},{"pid":"fde338ded2ad04d0186847b895fd28660df125fb","tid":151004,"uid":36329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:03:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n我食過藥丸, 一隻腳企出花槽, 用毛巾打圈綁係浴室近天花支柱上面<br />\n算唔算靜係想?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打介唔介意講下有咩困難？<br />\n<br />\nbetween我仲等緊樓主你同我講下有咩困難呀 如果你唔介意嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上年一月尾 同樣好多大學生跳樓 其中一個係我以前中學嘅同學 <br />\n雖然畢業後冇聯絡 但係偶爾都會諗起我去佢班房搵自己朋友玩個陣都會順便整蠱下佢<br />\n佢有抑鬱依樣嘢都係新聞報咗出來我先發覺 而佢係2015完結嘅時候（即係自殺前一個月）仲係facebook出過一個好積極嘅post 冇人諗過原來佢都有諗唔通嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n所以我希望如果有我可以幫忙嘅地方 而因此可以令想死嘅人少一個嘅話 我都想試下"},{"pid":"6419ef93c616a5640940811cc2f08471574c8d48","tid":151004,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:48:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我食過藥丸, 一隻腳企出花槽, 用毛巾打圈綁係浴室近天花支柱上面<br />\n算唔算靜係想?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打介唔介意講下有咩困難？<br />\n<br />\nbetween我仲等緊樓主你同我講下有咩困難呀 如果你唔介意嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上年一月尾 同樣好多大學生跳樓 其中一個係我以前中學嘅同學 <br />\n雖然畢業後冇聯絡 但係偶爾都會諗起我去佢班房搵自己朋友玩個陣都會順便整蠱下佢<br />\n佢有抑鬱依樣嘢都係新聞報咗出來我先發覺 而佢係2015完結嘅時候（即係自殺前一個月）仲係facebook出過一個好積極嘅post 冇人諗過原來佢都有諗唔通嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n所以我希望如果有我可以幫忙嘅地方 而因此可以令想死嘅人少一個嘅話 我都想試下</blockquote><br />\n自殺前一個月仲係facebook出過一個好積極嘅post <br />\n<br />\n迴光返照<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb8983918d57d0cd086424bc1829defcfbb9559","tid":151004,"uid":36329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:09:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n自殺前一個月仲係facebook出過一個好積極嘅post <br />\n<br />\n迴光返照<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽返校長講就話跳之前佢啱啱食完抑鬱藥<br />\n一時諗唔開就跳咗落去 都唔係佢自己控制到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3b0fef00780c1e3249816d4594a7936199dc2e","tid":151004,"uid":85619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T06:11:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我食過藥丸, 一隻腳企出花槽, 用毛巾打圈綁係浴室近天花支柱上面<br />\n算唔算靜係想?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打介唔介意講下有咩困難？<br />\n<br />\nbetween我仲等緊樓主你同我講下有咩困難呀 如果你唔介意嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上年一月尾 同樣好多大學生跳樓 其中一個係我以前中學嘅同學 <br />\n雖然畢業後冇聯絡 但係偶爾都會諗起我去佢班房搵自己朋友玩個陣都會順便整蠱下佢<br />\n佢有抑鬱依樣嘢都係新聞報咗出來我先發覺 而佢係2015完結嘅時候（即係自殺前一個月）仲係facebook出過一個好積極嘅post 冇人諗過原來佢都有諗唔通嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n所以我希望如果有我可以幫忙嘅地方 而因此可以令想死嘅人少一個嘅話 我都想試下</blockquote><br />\n我都明白你既感受，真係希望開解倒一個人得一個人，救倒一條生命得一條<br />\n<br />\n話說2010年我都有個之前既中學同學係屋企吊頸自殺，報紙話佢壓力大睇唔開，我覺得好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9bd9b7b84eecf822e064f13acaa060e02763a8b","tid":151004,"uid":64701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T06:18:47.000Z","msg":"大量報用多巴胺藥<br />\n強行令幸福感塞爆大腦<br />\n然後喺最幸福嘅情況下自殺<br />\n喺失去正常人判斷力下跳樓應該係最輕鬆"}]}